    public class LibBrowserChart
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements javax.swing.Scrollable
    This class creates a panel on which to draw family tree charts in a LibBrowser.

      • paintTree

        public void paintTree(java.awt.Graphics g)
        For every Individual, Family, and Link whose home chart is the current chartID, call their drawing methods. Put their symbol in the location indicated on their 'loation' field. Draw Ego in red, Alter in blue, and all linking kinsmen in orange.
        Parameters:
        g - the Graphics object on which to paint

      • writeLegend

        public void writeLegend(java.awt.Graphics g,
               int maxY)
        Write a legend on the bottom of each page of a diagram that uses letters instead of kin terms. Begin writing at 20, maxY.
        Parameters:
        g - the Graphics object on which to paint
        maxY - the vertical height
